collectible.name: Happy Valentine's Day, Origin City! From, Scarcity Gnomes' Confectionaries
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description: These days it seems like Scarcity Island is getting all the fun, but in the gnome bakery, we know who is really number 1. "Origin City, Origin City, Origin City!" they cry, as bakers collect sugar-rains from air dragons passing by. "OC Forever, OC Forever, OC Forever", they chant. "One day OC will do many things... many things we can't."
